{
  "id": 6369,
  "name": "Nicole",
  "desc": "<p>A prophetess and a member of the Hexenzirkel. She is also known as Nicole Reeyn and N. <span class=\"wk-shady\">She is, presumably, one of the last seelies who remained conscious. She lost her voice and can only talk inside people's heads.</span></p>",
